vstore.framework.file.events

Class FilesReadyEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • vstore.framework.file.events.FilesReadyEvent

  • public class FilesReadyEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    This event gets published when your file request you made to the framework is ready. If you want your app to get notified, you need to subscribe to this event.

        Constructs a new FilesReadyEvent.
        Parameters:
        fileList - A list containing the files from the database.
        onlyPendingFiles - Set this to true, if the event contains only files that have an upload pending.
        onlyPrivateFiles - Set this to true, if the event contains only private files.

        public boolean isOnlyPendingFiles()
